*******************************************************************************************************************
	EDITABLE PARAMETERS
*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************

/pageinstructions:			the instructions that appear at the top of each surveypage

<parameters>
/pageinstructions = "Please indicate how often the following statements apply to you by selecting the appropriate number from the scale below each item.
"
</parameters>

